{"tid":2141291,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"請問政府點解早排要開放社區中心俾人堂食？","createTime":"2020-08-05T14:12:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T14:13:51.000Z","uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3a2e40cf3915635683502d77bb6a7b2c562f1b45","tid":2141291,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T14:12:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200805/SSX4SA7A4FP2CLSV4DQQ4JL6NY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200805%2FSSX4SA7A4FP2CLSV4DQQ4JL6NY%2F&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2F%2BDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=632a6f8a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200805%2FSSX4SA7A4FP2CLSV4DQQ4JL6NY%2F&h=d9e42502\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200805/SSX4SA7A4FP2CLSV4DQQ4JL6NY/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-RAOsArBVUq1pBiVGP8ihiEyH3A=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CPVFDLFTOTSITYOWEDTB62BFIY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-RAOsArBVUq1pBiVGP8ihiEyH3A%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCPVFDLFTOTSITYOWEDTB62BFIY.jpg&h=50c22503&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府上周三實施全日禁堂食，市民難以找尋地方食飯，多間教會、商戶及學校等伸出援手，為有需要市民免費提供用膳場所，其中香港逸東酒店宣佈免費開放2樓宴會廳供市民在中午、晚上食飯。《蘋果》接獲一張逸東酒店的告示，提及因接到政府指示，要求在下午6時後關閉宴會廳，因而須取消晚上開放時段，並稱：「造成大家的不便，我們深感抱歉」。"},{"pid":"25dfd495849ab6593ccc67b1d61ea1788c3ec659","tid":2141291,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T14:13:51.000Z","msg":"【有圖】點解呢個靚仔咁後生就要揸柺杖？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2141275\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2141275</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}